  # User Management Endpoints
  
  All endpoints in this folder require Bearer token authentication.
  
  ## Profile Management (User Service)
  - Setup Profile - Complete profile after registration
  - Get My Profile - Retrieve current user's profile from User Service
  - Update My Profile - Partial update using PATCH
  - Get User by ID - View other users' profiles
  
  ## Auth Info (Auth Service)
  - Get My Auth Info - Get basic auth information from Auth Service (different from profile)
  
  ## User Discovery (User Service)
  - Get Suggested Users - Recommended users to follow
  - Get Available Users - All active users in system
  
  Gateway extracts userId from JWT and forwards to User Service via X-User-Id header.
}